bring shame to me.

776
01:35:07,272 --> 01:35:11,557
I shudder to recall how once long ago
I embraced the same beliefs...

777
01:35:11,620 --> 01:35:13,633
how at one time I was, in fact...

778
01:35:13,666 --> 01:35:17,693
