such a great lie.

863
01:48:59,628 --> 01:49:02,152
After all these years, you still
do not understand Tibetan ways.

864
01:49:03,369 --> 01:49:06,756
To return a gift is unforgivable.

865
01:49:09,665 --> 01:49:12,990
A man who betrays his culture
should not preach about its customs.

866
01:49:19,544 --> 01:49:22,326
There was a time
I would have wished you dead...

867
01:49:22,421 --> 01:49:24,562
but your shame
will be your torture.

868
01:49:24,689 --> 01:49:27,888
And your torture
will be your life.

869
01:49:27,951 --> 01:49:30,189
I wish it to be long.

870
01:49:41,474 --> 01:49:44,159
