them? What kind of leader would I be?

894
01:54:09,464 --> 01:54:11,638
I have to stay here.

895
01:54:11,702 --> 01:54:13,972
Serving others
is my path to liberation .

896
01:54:24,425 --> 01:54:27,303
- Then I don't go either.
- Why not?

897
